Barikothi: Located at the heart of West Bengal, this is Murshidabad’s First Heritage Hotel (300 years old), 200 kms away from Kolkata ~ PERFECT WEEKEND GETAWAY! (4hrs by Train & 6-7hrs by Car). Indulge in the heritage of the nawabs and zamindars of Bengal and make it a one of a kind experience.

@barikothi was built in the late 1700s. The name of the house, Bari Kothi literally means the Palace of the Elder, since it was the house of the elder (bari) brother, Rai Bahadur Budh Sing Dudhoria, a significant member of the Sheherwali community.

📍 Azimgani, Murshidabad
🌐 www.barikothi.com
💻 Bookings : +91 9051200800
🚗 5-6 hours by car
🚆 Train Station: Azimganj, Murdhidabad
🥗 Sheherwali Cuisine (Pure Veg)
